Class SlashCommandUpdater

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.ListenerAdapter
      • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.SlashCommandUpdater
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.EventListener
    public class SlashCommandUpdater
extends net.dv8tion.jda.api.hooks.ListenerAdapter
    Class that sends the SlashCommandData to Discord. Uses a CommandTree to properly transpile all CommandDefinitions to SlashCommandData.
    Since:
    2.3.0
    See Also:
    CommandTree
